solution.p:

    -3x+1 \amp \gt 7 \amp \amp \blert{\text{Subtract 1 from both sides.}}
        -3x \amp \gt 6  \amp \amp \blert{\text{Divide both sides by -3.}}
        x \amp \lt -2 \amp \amp \blert{\text{Reverse the direction of the inequality.}}
